channel.title: Please Help- I followed the tutorial but
channel.description:
It says
Note: stream.java uses or overrides deprecated API Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details Press any key to continue... (shutsdown)
So I ran with -Xlint:deprecation and the details are: stream.java:232: warning: [deprecation] getbytes<int,int,byte[],int> in java.lang.String has been deprecated s.getbytes<0, s.length<>, buffer, currentOffset.; ^ 1 warning Press any key to continue... (shutsdown)
Any help please?
